title: Operation Dalmation: A Tail-Waggin' Family Adventure!

sources.description:
Click here to watch great FREE Movies & TV: http://filmrise.com

What do you get when you cross a rambunctious girl, a nutty professor, a mischievous medicine man and a colorful dalmation with a stuffy dog show? Puppy pandemonium! Travel back in time with Grandma Julietta to her humble childhood, when she found her beloved Dalmatian, Baskerville. Join the outrageous cast of characters on this great big adventure!

#freemovies #moviesondemand #fullmovie

metadata.Plot: Jessica visits her grandparent's farm and finds seven puppies in the barn. She must save the farm and the puppies from a bank that is planning to take them away.
metadata.Actors: Mary Lucy Bivens, James K. Flynn, Cole Rosenbaum, Dustin Rubin
